settings.description: From boomerang pirouettes to rolling balls of pain .. just jump into the purely psychotic sand -- enemies and all. Made in August of '21 .. updated improvements over the last week.
Fun Fact: I'm terrible at making underwater levels, so I just decided to take out the water in the underwater, thus creating an... under level.
